OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FA father and son have been jailed for
OL,7,F30 years for killing a child in a high
OL,8,Fspeed hit and run on the A2 in Kent.
OL,10,FOwen Maughan, 27, was travelling at
OL,11,F60mph when he deliberately slammed his
OL,12,F4X4 vehicle into a pick-up truck
OL,13,Fcarrying four members of the same
OL,14,Ffamily, killing four year old Peter
OL,15,FMaughan.
OL,17,FOwen Maughan's father, Patrick
OL,18,FMaughan, 54, was accused of
OL,19,Fencouraging his son from the front
OL,20,Fpassenger seat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
