CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774519536
OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FToday at Maidstone Crown Court, Owen
OL,7,FMaughan was sentenced to 12 years and
OL,8,FPatrick Maughan was sentenced to 18
OL,9,Fyears behind bars.
OL,11,FThe court heard that Owen and Patrick
OL,12,FMaughan, both of Hill Rise in Darenth
OL,13,Fin Kent, "chased" the car down the A2
OL,14,Fin Kent for several miles.
OL,16,FThere was shouting between the two
OL,17,Fcars before Owen Maughan drove into
OL,18,Fthe wrong lane and clipped the Ford
OL,19,Fpick-up truck at about 60mph, and the
OL,20,Fcar rolled over multiple times, the
OL,21,Fcourt heard.
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@QO]
