PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774519536
OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FPeter Maughan was in the back of the
OL,7,Fcar with his one-year-old sister
OL,8,FAnnarica Mahon, while their mother
OL,9,FHayley, Owen Maughan's cousin, was in
OL,10,Fthe front passenger seat and her
OL,11,Fpartner Lovell Mahon was driving.
OL,13,FMr Mahon suffered serious injuries
OL,14,Fincluding a skull fracture and is
OL,15,Funlikely to walk again.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
