PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774519536
OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FOwen Maughan had previously admitted
OL,7,Finflicting grievous bodily harm on Mr
OL,8,FMahon - the jury also found Patrick
OL,9,FMaughan guilty of the same charge.
OL,11,FThe court had heard that Mr Mahon and
OL,12,FOwen Maughan had never met and he did
OL,13,Fnot associate with his cousin Hayley.
OL,15,FHayley Maughan filmed video clips of
OL,16,Fthe two men following them, leaving a
OL,17,Fvoice note for her mother Erica in
OL,18,Fwhich she said she was afraid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
