PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774519536
OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FGiving evidence during the trial, Owen
OL,7,FMaughan told jurors he did not know
OL,8,Fthere were children in the car.
OL,10,FHe said he believed he and Mr Mahon
OL,11,Fwere going to fight after arguing back
OL,12,Fand forth between the cars, and he
OL,13,Fdecided to dent the side of Mr Mahon's
OL,14,Fcar so he would stop and get out.
OL,16,FHe denied trying to cause serious
OL,17,Finjury.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
