PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774519536
OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FJurors heard the pair had been
OL,7,Fdrinking in Rochester earlier that
OL,8,Fday, and had about 12 bottles of beer
OL,9,Fand 13 pints respectively, before they
OL,10,Fbegan driving their Ford Ranger pick-
OL,11,Fup truck home.
OL,13,FA statement read to court from Mr
OL,14,FMahon described how hard it was living
OL,15,Feach day without his son and in a
OL,16,Fwheelchair.
OL,18,F"Life will never be the same," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@^O]
