PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774519536
OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,F"The death of Peter has broken me, he
OL,7,Fwas too good for this world. When I
OL,8,Ffound out he was gone words can't even
OL,9,Fdescribe it.
OL,11,F"I can't even get to see Peter at his
OL,12,Fgrave because of the bumps."
OL,14,FHe said his rehabilitation is a "full-
OL,15,Ftime job" and Ms Maughan added that as
OL,16,Fsoon as that "horrible" day happened,
OL,17,Fshe became a nurse.
