OL,3,CFather and son jailed for 30 years for
OL,4,Ckilling boy, 4, in hit and run
OL,6,FIn her statement she said Mr Mahon now
OL,7,Fhas bad anxiety and paranoia,
OL,8,Fincluding panicking if someone drives
OL,9,Ftoo close to them.
